on:\"sessionId\"`\n    EntryPoints      []SandboxEntryPoint   `json:\"entryPoints\"`\n    Status           string                `json:\"status\"`           // \"pending\", \"running\", \"failed\"\n    CreatedAt        time.Time             `json:\"createdAt\"`\n    ExpiresAt        time.Time             `json:\"expiresAt\"`\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## Integration with client-go\n\n| Component | Usage |\n|-----------|-------|\n| `clientset/versioned.Interface` | Get typed client for AgentRuntime/CodeInterpreter |\n| `informers/externalversions.SharedInformerFactory` | Informer lifecycle management |\n| `listers/runtime/v1alpha1.AgentRuntimeLister` | Read-only AgentRuntime queries |\n| `listers/runtime/v1alpha1.CodeInterpreterLister` | Read-only CodeInterpreter queries |\n| `fake.Clientset` | Unit test mocks |\n\n---\n\n## Notes\n\n- Watcher MUST be registered BEFORE creating the CR to avoid race conditions where Sandbox enters running before watcher is ready\n- Store placeholder MUST be created BEFORE CR creation for idempotency and rollback\n- Dynamic client is used for Sandbox/SandboxClaim CRDs (external to agentcube)\n- Per-user K8s client is used when authentication is enabled\n- All timeouts are configurable via constants in `defaults.go`\n- EntryPoints are built from `spec.Ports` with format: `{PathPrefix, Protocol, PodIP:Port}`\n","exit":0,"description":"Check delta-spec.md file ending","truncated":false},"title":"Check delta-spec.md file ending","time":{"start":1775846461757,"end":1775846461771}}}}
