{"type":"text","timestamp":1775846482627,"sessionID":"ses_28752f7a2ffeaJZJbHq9rT1whF","part":{"id":"prt_d78b2af9b001L1XIQlCS3ksc7P","messageID":"msg_d78b2917f0016DXSSKsmxNYUW2","sessionID":"ses_28752f7a2ffeaJZJbHq9rT1whF","type":"text","text":"The `delta-spec.md` file has been created successfully at `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-005/delta-spec.md`.\n\n## Summary\n\nThe delta specification for **AR-005 вҖ” Sandbox еҲӣе»әеӨ„зҗҶеҷЁ** includes:\n\n### Requirements with GIVEN/WHEN/THEN Scenarios:\n1. **AgentRuntime Sandbox Creation Endpoint** - 6 scenarios covering success, missing template, not found, invalid JSON, and missing fields\n2. **CodeInterpreter Sandbox Creation Endpoint** - 5 scenarios including warm pool vs full sandbox paths\n3. **Sandbox Object Building** - 5 scenarios for metadata, lifecycle, auth mode, and SandboxClaim\n4. **Sandbox Creation and Wait Flow** - 8 scenarios covering watcher registration, waiting, timeout, and Pod IP resolution\n5. **Rollback and Cleanup** - 4 scenarios for different failure conditions\n6. **Request Validation** - 4 scenarios for validation rules\n7. **Response Building** - 1 scenario for response format\n8. **Authentication Integration** - 4 scenarios for auth middleware\n9. **Idempotency** - 1 scenario for duplicate requests\n10. **Error Handling and HTTP Status Mapping** - 5 scenarios for error mapping\n11. **Context Propagation** - 2 scenarios\n12. **Timeout Configuration** - 2 scenarios\n\n### Additional Sections:\n- **File Index** - 11 source files and 4 test files\n- **Dependencies** - 7 key dependencies including client-go\n- **API Endpoints** - POST `/v1/agent-runtime` and POST `/v1/code-interpreter`\n- **Data Types** - CreateSandboxRequest, CreateSandboxResponse, SandboxInfo\n- **Integration with client-go** - 5 key components\n- **Notes** - 5 important implementation notes","time":{"start":1775846482624,"end":1775846482624}}}
